Brooklyn Beckham, 23, and his wife Nicola Peltz, 27, looked loved up as they headed out to a Los Angeles farmers market on Sunday. The couple chatted as they walked through the market and Brooklyn even picked out a beautiful bunch of pink flowers for his bride.The newlyweds looked casual with Brooklyn wearing blue jeans paired with a white T-shirt and trainers.The eldest son of David and Victoria added a black cap and some dark sunglasses as he picked up groceries.Nicola looked elegant in a backless black maxi dress paired with some platform heels.Her blonde tresses were left down and she shielded her eyes from the California sun with some sunglasses.She clutched the flowers Brooklyn had picked for her as he walked alongside her with his hand placed on her back.